{"tid":1813993,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔兔要做腫瘤手術, 做不做好?","createTime":"2020-01-06T16:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T03:23:25.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92077b5cce00bcd1cad7c1998bedfb1ae5de264f","tid":1813993,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:11:06.000Z","msg":"兔兔已有8歲，醫生發現腫瘤在頸部，有些兔仔手術後沒有再起身，尤其是老兔，究竟做不做好? 🤔 (兔子是好脆弱) 醫生不肯定是否癌細胞，但希望不是:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TYmktQp80eI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTYmktQp80eI&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=d56b1d05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TYmktQp80eI</a>"},{"pid":"522ec63c1cc61e7af4c8b6c80368c02e1672b39c","tid":1813993,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"又係你啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d55d7aff949698ef1d6d0314e85db6f4cebf64","tid":1813993,"uid":88587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"做，如果唔做你會後悔一世"},{"pid":"213f27a5dc1dd15927c53bea193c3fb582f78762","tid":1813993,"uid":108228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"睇左邊個醫生？醫生點講"},{"pid":"96d99f62be2823ab7197fe97d8bcad8e5f7fc5b3","tid":1813993,"uid":100016,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:45:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母收皮啦，又拎人地野當自己親身經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陷家鏟啦去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935ce9fcf5ffe460ae30791bbc19fc2e662aef7a","tid":1813993,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"終於決定了做手術，麻醉針藥力過後兔子終於起返身:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xcA1nWLYZF8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxcA1nWLYZF8&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=b82b7c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xcA1nWLYZF8</a>"},{"pid":"4e530246d5d7bedd69ab712d32cbaa6c2c35e22d","tid":1813993,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:44:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>兔兔的視覺好特別</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</em></span>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>你在牠後面也會看到你</em></span>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WGN1HtIEHxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWGN1HtIEHxA&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=eb65c1bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WGN1HtIEHxA</a>"},{"pid":"991cf154795444ffbcff5da8f28a7255cfe5c0da","tid":1813993,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"935ce9fcf5ffe460ae30791bbc19fc2e662aef7a","tid":1813993,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"終於決定了做手術，麻醉針藥力過後兔子終於起返身:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xcA1nWLYZF8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxcA1nWLYZF8&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=b82b7c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xcA1nWLYZF8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:23:25.000Z","msg":"恢復程度幾好，暫時給牠一個有限度地方，用圍欄圍住，等佢唔好周圍跳，整傷連針的傷口:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dbL64qnSY14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdbL64qnSY14&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=3a4a4430\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dbL64qnSY14</a>"}]}